<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN">
<html>
<head>
<title>Help: Setting up manager notification options</title>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=iso-8859-1">
<link href="../style.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
</head>

<body>
<p class="titlebold">Setting up managers to approve PO accounts</p>
<p class="text">If the order site accepts PO accounts, when a request is made
  to set up a PO account any given number of managers can be notified that a
request has been made. Generally, only one manager would need to be notified.</p>
<p class="text">To set up a PO approval manager, select Browse under Users in
  the main VariaPrint&#8482; Manager menu, and select &quot;Manager accounts&quot;. Add a new
  manager or select Access/Notification Options... from an existing manager and
  check the &quot;Approve PO Account Requests&quot; and &quot;Notify on PO Account Reqest&quot; options.</p>
</body>
</html>
